line_1: Which Thy own Hand had whilom planted,
line_2: Both pleas'd with all we thought We wanted:

line_1: For what has Virro painted, built, and planted?
line_2: Only to shew how many Tastes he wanted.

line_1: 'Twas hung round with woodbine my Jessy had planted
line_2: When distant one bower my fancy still haunted,
